      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so it's basically just the sugars and proteins reacting together right? is there anything else that affects how intense that reaction gets, like pH levels or something? i feel like my instructor keep mentioning the environment inside the oven matters also.",
      "source": "evaluator"
